 them by closely keeping in touch with them','A “pull” selling strategy is one that requires high spending on advertising and promotion to build up consumer demand for a product. ... A “Profile” strategy takes time and isn\'t something that can be changed overnight. Your profile is linked to positioning and identity – it is how your stakeholders view you.','A communication strategy guides an entire program or intervention. It sets the tone and direction so that all communication activities, products and materials work in harmony to achieve the desired change. Strategic activities and materials are more likely to promote change.',_binary '\0','2021-08-09 12:21:17',NULL,'CREATED_BY',NULL,NULL),(25,106,208,'Testing by Business Users','2021-08-11 00:00:00','2021-08-31 00:00:00','Testing by Business Users','','','',_binary '\0','2021-08-13 16:39:58',NULL,'CREATED_BY',NULL,NULL),(26,107,209,'Testing by Business Users','2021-08-16 00:00:00','2021-09-30 00:00:00','Testing by Business Users','Testing by Business Users','','',_binary '\0','2021-08-17 15:24:59',NULL,'CREATED_BY',NULL,NULL),(27,108,213,'Sales call reporting refers to the information a salesperson documents after a call for future reference. The sales call report makes it easy to keep track of the calls and correspondence that takes place between sales reps and leads. These reports offer sales leaders insight into individual reps and team performance.','2021-08-02 00:00:00','2021-08-31 00:00:00','Officers try to stop the calls by either warning or arresting the harasser. With both Call Trace and a Trap, your phone conversations are not listened to or recorded by the phone company.','Calling someone over 25 times over 24 hours (1 day) in this case is considered harassment. What you can do is to warn the person to stop calling you. If they keep calling you, do not hesitate to block and report them.','Here are the main sections of the standard report writing format: Title Section – This includes the name of the author(s) and the date of report preparation. Summary – There needs to be a summary of the major points, conclusions, and recommendations.','A formal report is an official report that contains detailed information, research, and data necessary to make business decisions. Some examples are annual reports, expense reports, incident reports, and even safety reports. ... Keep in mind that your formal report should be clear and free of distracting language',_binary '\0','2021-08-22 22:35:29',NULL,'CREATED_BY',NULL,NULL),(28,109,213,'A call report is a regulatory report that must be filed by banks in the U.S','2021-08-22 00:00:00','2021-09-30 00:00:00','Nowadays, these reports of balance sheet and income statement information are filed quarterly;','A daily call report is used to organize the call transactions and other related activities','Report of Condition is a bank\'s balance sheet, which lists the assets, liabilities','The call summary page provides a high-level view of how the conversation with a customer went,&nbsp;',_binary '\0','2021-08-23 11:08:02',NULL,'CREATED_BY',NULL,NULL),(29,111,229,'Workflow testing','2021-09-30 00:00:00','2021-09-22 00:00:00','Workflow testing','Workflow testing','','',_binary '\0','2021-09-02 11:50:52',NULL,'CREATED_BY',NULL,NULL),(30,115,114,'wsdhgtrewasgd','2021-09-17 00:00:00','2021-09-15 00:00:00','','','','',_binary '\0','2021-09-03 15:42:12',NULL,'CREATED_BY',NULL,NULL),(31,116,120,'','2021-09-02 00:00:00','2021-09-01 00:00:00','','','','',_binary '\0','2021-09-05 15:00:27',NULL,'CREATED_BY',NULL,NULL),(32,117,120,'In English writing, quotation marks or inverted commas, also known informally as quotes, talking marks, speech marks, quote marks, quotemarks or speechmarks, are punctuation marks placed on either side of a word or phrase in order to identify it as a quotation, direct speech or a literal title or name.','2021-09-02 00:00:00','2021-09-01 00:00:00','','','','',_binary '\0','2021-09-05 15:05:19',NULL,'CREATED_BY',NULL,NULL),(